 315    def sql_access(self, db_name=None, username=None, password=None, hostname=None):
 316        """This is where you access the database
 317        """
 318        self.db = access_database(db_name, username, password, hostname)
 319        self.db['db'].transaction()
 320
 321        self.events_model = EventsModel(self.db)
 322
 323        self.events_view.setModel(self.events_model)
 324        self.events_view.hideColumn(0)
 325
 326        self.channels_model = QSqlTableModel(self, self.db['db'])
 327        self.channels_model.setTable('channels')
 328        self.channels_view.setModel(self.channels_model)
 329        self.channels_view.hideColumn(0)
 330
 331        self.electrodes_model = QSqlTableModel(self, self.db['db'])
 332        self.electrodes_model.setTable('electrodes')
 333        self.electrodes_view.setModel(self.electrodes_model)
 334        self.electrodes_view.hideColumn(0)
 335
 336        self.list_subjects()
 337
 338    def sql_commit(self):
 339        self.db['db'].commit()
 340        self.setWindowTitle('')
 341        self.unsaved_changes = False
 342        self.db['db'].transaction()
 343
 344    def sql_rollback(self):
 345        self.db['db'].rollback()
 346        self.unsaved_changes = False
 347        self.setWindowTitle('')
 348        self.db['db'].transaction()
 349        self.list_subjects()

 351    def list_subjects(self, code_to_select=None):
 352        """
 353        code_to_select : str
 354            code of the subject to select
 355        """
 356        for line in self.lists.values():
 357            line.clear()
 358
 359        to_select = None
 360        if self.subjsort.isChecked():
 361            args = {
 362                'alphabetical': True,
 363                'reverse': False,
 364                }
 365        else:
 366            args = {
 367                'alphabetical': False,
 368                'reverse': True,
 369                }
 370        for subj in list_subjects(self.db, **args):
 371            item = QListWidgetItem(str(subj))
 372            if subj.id in self.search.subjects:
 373                highlight(item)
 374            item.setData(Qt.UserRole, subj)
 375            self.lists['subjects'].addItem(item)
 376            if code_to_select is not None and code_to_select == str(subj):
 377                to_select = item
 378            if to_select is None:  # select first one
 379                to_select = item
 380        self.lists['subjects'].setCurrentItem(to_select)
 381
 382    @pyqtSlot(QListWidgetItem, QListWidgetItem)
 383    def proc_all(self, current=None, previous=None, item=None):
 384        """GUI calls current and previous. You can call item"""
 385
 386        self.list_channels_electrodes()
 387        if item is None:
 388            # when clicking on a previously selected list, it sends a signal where current is None, but I don't understand why
 389            if current is None:
 390                return
 391            item = current.data(Qt.UserRole)
 392
 393        if item.t == 'subject':
 394            self.list_sessions_and_protocols(item)
 395
 396        elif item.t == 'session':
 397            self.list_runs(item)
 398
 399        elif item.t == 'protocol':
 400            pass
 401
 402        elif item.t == 'run':
 403            self.list_recordings(item)
 404            self.show_events(item)
 405
 406        elif item.t == 'recording':
 407            self.list_channels_electrodes(item)
 408
 409        self.list_params()
 410        self.list_files()

 412    def list_sessions_and_protocols(self, subj=None):
 413
 414        if subj is None or subj is False:
 415            subj = self.current('subjects')
 416
 417        for level, l in self.lists.items():
 418            if level in ('subjects', ):
 419                continue
 420            l.clear()
 421
 422        for sess in subj.list_sessions():
 423            item = QListWidgetItem_time(sess, _session_name(sess))
 424            if sess.id in self.search.sessions:
 425                highlight(item)
 426            self.lists['sessions'].addItem(item)
 427        self.lists['sessions'].setCurrentRow(0)
 428
 429        for protocol in subj.list_protocols():
 430            item = QListWidgetItem(_protocol_name(protocol))
 431            item.setData(Qt.UserRole, protocol)
 432            self.lists['protocols'].addItem(item)
 433        self.lists['protocols'].setCurrentRow(0)
 434
 435    def list_runs(self, sess=None):
 436
 437        if sess is None or sess is False:
 438            sess = self.current('sessions')
 439
 440        for level, l in self.lists.items():
 441            if level in ('subjects', 'sessions', 'protocols'):
 442                continue
 443            l.clear()
 444
 445        for i, run in enumerate(sess.list_runs()):
 446            item = QListWidgetItem_time(run, f'#{i + 1: 3d}: {run.task_name}')
 447            if run.id in self.search.runs:
 448                highlight(item)
 449            self.lists['runs'].addItem(item)
 450        self.lists['runs'].setCurrentRow(0)
 451
 452    def list_recordings(self, run=None):
 453
 454        if run is None or run is False:
 455            run = self.current('runs')
 456
 457        for level, l in self.lists.items():
 458            if level in ('subjects', 'sessions', 'protocols', 'runs'):
 459                continue
 460            l.clear()
 461
 462        for recording in run.list_recordings():
 463            item = QListWidgetItem(recording.modality)
 464            item.setData(Qt.UserRole, recording)
 465            if recording.id in self.search.recordings:
 466                highlight(item)
 467            self.lists['recordings'].addItem(item)
 468        self.lists['recordings'].setCurrentRow(0)
 469
 470    def list_channels_electrodes(self, recording=None):
 471
 472        for level, l in self.lists.items():
 473            if level in ('channels', 'electrodes'):
 474                l.clear()
 475
 476        self.channels_model.setFilter('channel_group_id = 0')
 477        self.channels_model.select()
 478        self.channels_view.setEnabled(False)
 479        self.electrodes_model.setFilter('electrode_group_id = 0')
 480        self.electrodes_model.select()
 481        self.electrodes_view.setEnabled(False)
 482        self.elec_form.clearContents()
 483
 484        if recording is None:
 485            return
 486
 487        sess = self.current('sessions')
 488
 489        if recording.modality in ('ieeg', 'eeg', 'meg'):
 490            for chan in sess.list_channels():
 491                item = QListWidgetItem(_name(chan.name))
 492                item.setData(Qt.UserRole, chan)
 493                self.lists['channels'].addItem(item)
 494
 495            for elec in sess.list_electrodes():
 496                item = QListWidgetItem(_name(elec.name))
 497                item.setData(Qt.UserRole, elec)
 498                self.lists['electrodes'].addItem(item)
 499
 500    def statusbar_selected(self):
 501
 502        statusbar = []
 503        for k, v in self.lists.items():
 504            item = v.currentItem()
 505            if item is None:
 506                continue
 507            obj = item.data(Qt.UserRole)
 508            statusbar.append(repr(obj))
 509
 510        self.statusBar().showMessage('\t'.join(statusbar))
 511
 512    def list_params(self):
 513        self.statusbar_selected()
 514
 515        self.t_params.blockSignals(True)
 516        self.t_params.clearContents()
 517
 518        all_params = []
 519        for k, v in self.lists.items():
 520            item = v.currentItem()
 521            if item is None:
 522                continue
 523            obj = item.data(Qt.UserRole)
 524
 525            parameters = {}
 526            parameters.update(list_parameters(self, obj))
 527
 528            if k == 'runs':
 529                w = Popup_Experimenters(obj, self)
 530                parameters.update({'Experimenters': w})
 531                w = Popup_Protocols(obj, self)
 532                parameters.update({'Protocols': w})
 533                if obj.task_name == 'top_up':
 534                    w = Popup_IntendedFor(obj, self)
 535                    parameters.update({'Intended For': w})
 536
 537            elif k == 'recordings':
 538
 539                if obj.modality in ('ieeg', 'eeg', 'meg'):
 540                    parameters.update(list_parameters(self, obj))
 541
 542                    sess = self.current('sessions')
 543
 544                    w = QComboBox()  # add callback here
 545                    w.addItem('(undefined channels)', None)
 546                    for chan in sess.list_channels():
 547                        w.addItem(_name(chan.name), chan)
 548                    channels = obj.channels
 549                    if channels is None:
 550                        w.setCurrentText('')
 551                    else:
 552                        w.setCurrentText(_name(channels.name))
 553                    w.activated.connect(partial(self.combo_chanelec, widget=w))
 554                    parameters.update({'Channels': w})
 555
 556                    w = QComboBox()
 557                    w.addItem('(undefined electrodes)', None)
 558                    for elec in sess.list_electrodes():
 559                        w.addItem(_name(elec.name), elec)
 560                    electrodes = obj.electrodes
 561                    if electrodes is None:
 562                        w.setCurrentText('')
 563                    else:
 564                        w.setCurrentText(_name(electrodes.name))
 565                    w.activated.connect(partial(self.combo_chanelec, widget=w))
 566                    parameters.update({'Electrodes': w})
 567
 568            for p_k, p_v in parameters.items():
 569                all_params.append({
 570                    'level': self.groups[k].title(),
 571                    'parameter': p_k,
 572                    'value': p_v,
 573                    })
 574
 575        self.t_params.setRowCount(len(all_params))
 576
 577        for i, val in enumerate(all_params):
 578            item = QTableWidgetItem(val['level'])
 579            item.setFlags(Qt.ItemIsSelectable | Qt.ItemIsEnabled)
 580            item.setBackground(QBrush(QColor('lightGray')))
 581            self.t_params.setItem(i, 0, item)
 582            item = QTableWidgetItem(val['parameter'])
 583            item.setFlags(Qt.ItemIsSelectable | Qt.ItemIsEnabled)
 584            self.t_params.setItem(i, 1, item)
 585            item = QTableWidgetItem(str(val['value']))
 586            self.t_params.setCellWidget(i, 2, val['value'])
 587
 588        self.t_params.blockSignals(False)
 589
 590    def combo_chanelec(self, i, widget):
 591        data = widget.currentData()
 592        recording = self.current('recordings')
 593        if data is None:
 594            if widget.currentText() == '(undefined channels)':
 595                recording.detach_channels()
 596            else:
 597                recording.detach_electrodes()
 598
 599        elif data.t == 'channel_group':

 618    def list_files(self):
 619
 620        self.t_files.blockSignals(True)
 621        self.t_files.clearContents()
 622
 623        all_files = []
 624        for k, v in self.lists.items():
 625            item = v.currentItem()
 626            if item is None:
 627                continue
 628            obj = item.data(Qt.UserRole)
 629            for file in obj.list_files():
 630                all_files.append({
 631                    'level': self.groups[k].title(),
 632                    'format': file.format,
 633                    'path': file.path,
 634                    'obj': [obj, file],
 635                    })
 636
 637        self.t_files.setRowCount(len(all_files))
 638
 639        for i, val in enumerate(all_files):
 640
 641            item = QTableWidgetItem(val['level'])
 642            item.setFlags(Qt.ItemIsSelectable | Qt.ItemIsEnabled)
 643            item.setBackground(QBrush(QColor('lightGray')))
 644            item.setData(Qt.UserRole, val['obj'])
 645            self.t_files.setItem(i, 0, item)
 646
 647            item = QTableWidgetItem(val['format'])
 648            item.setData(Qt.UserRole, val['obj'])
 649            self.t_files.setItem(i, 1, item)
 650
 651            item = QTableWidgetItem(str(val['path']))
 652            try:
 653                path_exists = val['path'].exists()
 654
 655            except PermissionError as err:
 656                lg.warning(err)
 657                item.setForeground(QBrush(QColor('orange')))
 658
 659            else:
 660                if not path_exists:
 661                    item.setForeground(QBrush(QColor('red')))
 662
 663            item.setData(Qt.UserRole, val['obj'])
 664            self.t_files.setItem(i, 2, item)
 665
 666        self.t_files.blockSignals(False)

 969    def do_export(self, checked=None):
 970
 971        subset = {'subjects': [], 'sessions': [], 'runs': []}
 972        run_ids = '(' + ', '.join([str(x['run_id']) for x in self.exports]) + ')'
 973
 974        query = QSqlQuery(self.db['db'])
 975        query.prepare(f"""\
 976            SELECT subjects.id, sessions.id, runs.id FROM runs
 977            JOIN sessions ON sessions.id = runs.session_id
 978            JOIN subjects ON subjects.id = sessions.subject_id
 979            WHERE runs.id IN {run_ids}
 980            """)
 981
 982        if not query.exec():
 983            raise SyntaxError(query.lastError().text())
 984
 985        while query.next():
 986            subset['subjects'].append(query.value(0))
 987            subset['sessions'].append(query.value(1))
 988            subset['runs'].append(query.value(2))
 989
 990        data_path = QFileDialog.getExistingDirectory()
 991        if data_path == '':
 992            return
 993
 994        progress = QProgressDialog('', 'Cancel', 0, len(subset['runs']), self)
 995        progress.setWindowTitle('Converting to BIDS')
 996        progress.setMinimumDuration(0)
 997        progress.setWindowModality(Qt.WindowModal)
 998
 999        create_bids(self.db, Path(data_path), deface=False, subset=subset, progress=progress)
1000        progress.setValue(len(subset['runs']))

1148    def calculate_offset(self):
1149        warning_title = 'Cannot calculate offset'
1150        run = self.current('runs')
1151        recordings = run.list_recordings()
1152
1153        if len(recordings) == 0:
1154            QMessageBox.warning(self, warning_title, 'There are no recordings')
1155            return
1156
1157        rec_fixed = recordings[0]
1158        rec_moving = self.current('recordings')
1159        if rec_fixed.id == rec_moving.id:
1160            QMessageBox.warning(self, warning_title, 'This function compares the first recording with the highlighted recording. Please select another recording to compute the offset')
1161            return
1162
1163        file_fixed = find_one_file(rec_fixed, ('blackrock', 'micromed', 'bci2000'))
1164        if file_fixed is None:
1165            QMessageBox.warning(self, warning_title, 'The first recording does not have an ephys file')
1166            return
1167        file_moving = find_one_file(rec_moving, ('blackrock', 'micromed', 'bci2000'))
1168        if file_moving is None:
1169            QMessageBox.warning(self, warning_title, 'The selected recording does not have an ephys file')
1170            return
1171
1172        calcoffset = CalculateOffset(self, file_fixed, file_moving)
1173        result = calcoffset.exec()
1174        if result:
1175            text = calcoffset.offset.text()
1176            if text.endswith(')'):
1177                return
1178            offset = float(text[:-1])
1179            rec_moving.offset = offset
1180
1181            self.list_params()
1182            self.modified()

1316    def io_electrodes(self):
1317
1318        mat_file = QFileDialog.getOpenFileName(
1319            self,
1320            "Open File",
1321            None,
1322            "Matlab (*.mat)")[0]
1323
1324        if mat_file == '':
1325            return
1326
1327        rec = self.current('recordings')
1328        chan = rec.channels
1329        chan_data = chan.data
1330        idx = isin(chan_data['type'], ('ECOG', 'SEEG'))
1331        n_chan = idx.sum()
1332        lg.warning(f'# of ECOG/SEEG channels for this recording: {n_chan}')
1333
1334        xyz = import_electrodes(mat_file, n_chan)
1335        if xyz is None:
1336            print('you need to do this manually')
1337            return
1338
1339        elec = Electrodes.add(self.db)
1340        elec_data = elec.empty(n_chan)
1341        elec_data['name'] = chan_data['name'][idx]
1342        elec_data['x'] = xyz[:, 0]
1343        elec_data['y'] = xyz[:, 1]
1344        elec_data['z'] = xyz[:, 2]
1345        elec.data = elec_data
1346        rec.attach_electrodes(elec)
1347
1348        self.modified()
1349        self.list_recordings()

1376def list_parameters(parent, obj):
1377    db = parent.db
1378
1379    columns = collect_columns(db, obj=obj)
1380
1381    d = {}
1382    for col, t in columns.items():
1383        col_info = db['tables'][t][col]
1384
1385        if not (col_info['index'] is False):
1386            continue
1387
1388        value = getattr(obj, col)
1389
1390        if col_info['type'] == 'QDateTime':
1391            w = make_datetime(value)
1392            w.dateTimeChanged.connect(partial(parent.changed, obj, col))
1393
1394        elif col_info['type'] == 'QDate':
1395            w = make_date(value)
1396            w.dateChanged.connect(partial(parent.changed, obj, col))
1397
1398        elif col_info['type'] == 'double':
1399            w = make_float(value)
1400            w.valueChanged.connect(partial(parent.changed, obj, col))
1401
1402        elif col_info['type'] == 'int':
1403            w = make_integer(value)
1404            w.valueChanged.connect(partial(parent.changed, obj, col))
1405
1406        elif col_info['type'] == 'QString':
1407            if col_info['values']:
1408                values = col_info['values']
1409                if len(values) > 20:
1410                    values = sorted(values)
1411                w = make_combobox(value, values)
1412
1413                w.currentTextChanged.connect(partial(parent.changed, obj, col))
1414            else:
1415                w = make_edit(value)
1416                w.editingFinished.connect(partial(parent.changed, obj, col, w))
1417
1418        else:
1419            raise ValueError(f'unknown type "{col_info["type"]}"')
1420
1421        if col_info['doc'] is not None:
1422            w.setToolTip(col_info['doc'])
1423
1424        d[col_info['alias']] = w
1425
1426    return d

 352    def list_subjects(self, code_to_select=None):
 353        """
 354        code_to_select : str
 355            code of the subject to select
 356        """
 357        for line in self.lists.values():
 358            line.clear()
 359
 360        to_select = None
 361        if self.subjsort.isChecked():
 362            args = {
 363                'alphabetical': True,
 364                'reverse': False,
 365                }
 366        else:
 367            args = {
 368                'alphabetical': False,
 369                'reverse': True,
 370                }
 371        for subj in list_subjects(self.db, **args):
 372            item = QListWidgetItem(str(subj))
 373            if subj.id in self.search.subjects:
 374                highlight(item)
 375            item.setData(Qt.UserRole, subj)
 376            self.lists['subjects'].addItem(item)
 377            if code_to_select is not None and code_to_select == str(subj):
 378                to_select = item
 379            if to_select is None:  # select first one
 380                to_select = item
 381        self.lists['subjects'].setCurrentItem(to_select)

 513    def list_params(self):
 514        self.statusbar_selected()
 515
 516        self.t_params.blockSignals(True)
 517        self.t_params.clearContents()
 518
 519        all_params = []
 520        for k, v in self.lists.items():
 521            item = v.currentItem()
 522            if item is None:
 523                continue

 525
 526            parameters = {}

 545                    w = QComboBox()  # add callback here
 546                    w.addItem('(undefined channels)', None)
 547                    for chan in sess.list_channels():
 548                        w.addItem(_name(chan.name), chan)
 549                    channels = obj.channels
 550                    if channels is None:
 551                        w.setCurrentText('')
 552                    else:
 553                        w.setCurrentText(_name(channels.name))
 554                    w.activated.connect(partial(self.combo_chanelec, widget=w))
 555                    parameters.update({'Channels': w})
 556
 557                    w = QComboBox()
 558                    w.addItem('(undefined electrodes)', None)
 559                    for elec in sess.list_electrodes():
 560                        w.addItem(_name(elec.name), elec)
 561                    electrodes = obj.electrodes
 562                    if electrodes is None:
 563                        w.setCurrentText('')
 564                    else:
 565                        w.setCurrentText(_name(electrodes.name))
 566                    w.activated.connect(partial(self.combo_chanelec, widget=w))
 567                    parameters.update({'Electrodes': w})

 571                    'level': self.groups[k].title(),
 572                    'parameter': p_k,
 573                    'value': p_v,

 585            self.t_params.setItem(i, 1, item)

 669    def changed(self, obj, column, x):
 670        if isinstance(x, QDate):
 671            x = x.toPyDate()
 672        elif isinstance(x, QDateTime):
 673            x = x.toPyDateTime()
 674        else:
 675            if isinstance(x, QLineEdit):
 676                x = x.text()
 677
 678            if x == NULL_TEXT:
 679                x = None
 680            else:
 681                x = f'{x}'
 682
 683        setattr(obj, column, x)
 684        self.modified()

 970    def do_export(self, checked=None):
 971
 972        subset = {'subjects': [], 'sessions': [], 'runs': []}
 973        run_ids = '(' + ', '.join([str(x['run_id']) for x in self.exports]) + ')'
 974
 975        query = QSqlQuery(self.db['db'])
 976        query.prepare(f"""\
 977            SELECT subjects.id, sessions.id, runs.id FROM runs
 978            JOIN sessions ON sessions.id = runs.session_id
 979            JOIN subjects ON subjects.id = sessions.subject_id
 980            WHERE runs.id IN {run_ids}
 981            """)
 982
 983        if not query.exec():
 984            raise SyntaxError(query.lastError().text())
 985
 986        while query.next():
 987            subset['subjects'].append(query.value(0))
 988            subset['sessions'].append(query.value(1))
 989            subset['runs'].append(query.value(2))
 990
 991        data_path = QFileDialog.getExistingDirectory()
 992        if data_path == '':
 993            return
 994
 995        progress = QProgressDialog('', 'Cancel', 0, len(subset['runs']), self)
 996        progress.setWindowTitle('Converting to BIDS')
 997        progress.setMinimumDuration(0)
 998        progress.setWindowModality(Qt.WindowModal)
 999
1000        create_bids(self.db, Path(data_path), deface=False, subset=subset, progress=progress)
1001        progress.setValue(len(subset['runs']))
1002

1149    def calculate_offset(self):
1150        warning_title = 'Cannot calculate offset'
1151        run = self.current('runs')
1152        recordings = run.list_recordings()
1153
1154        if len(recordings) == 0:
1155            QMessageBox.warning(self, warning_title, 'There are no recordings')
1156            return
1157
1158        rec_fixed = recordings[0]
1159        rec_moving = self.current('recordings')
1160        if rec_fixed.id == rec_moving.id:
1161            QMessageBox.warning(self, warning_title, 'This function compares the first recording with the highlighted recording. Please select another recording to compute the offset')
1162            return
1163
1164        file_fixed = find_one_file(rec_fixed, ('blackrock', 'micromed', 'bci2000'))
1165        if file_fixed is None:
1166            QMessageBox.warning(self, warning_title, 'The first recording does not have an ephys file')
1167            return
1168        file_moving = find_one_file(rec_moving, ('blackrock', 'micromed', 'bci2000'))
1169        if file_moving is None:
1170            QMessageBox.warning(self, warning_title, 'The selected recording does not have an ephys file')
1171            return
1172
1173        calcoffset = CalculateOffset(self, file_fixed, file_moving)
1174        result = calcoffset.exec()
1175        if result:
1176            text = calcoffset.offset.text()
1177            if text.endswith(')'):
1178                return
1179            offset = float(text[:-1])
1180            rec_moving.offset = offset
1181
1182            self.list_params()
1183            self.modified()

def do_export(self, checked=None): 
 970    def do_export(self, checked=None):
 971
 972        subset = {'subjects': [], 'sessions': [], 'runs': []}
 973        run_ids = '(' + ', '.join([str(x['run_id']) for x in self.exports]) + ')'
 974
 975        query = QSqlQuery(self.db['db'])
 976        query.prepare(f"""\
 977            SELECT subjects.id, sessions.id, runs.id FROM runs
 978            JOIN sessions ON sessions.id = runs.session_id
 979            JOIN subjects ON subjects.id = sessions.subject_id
 980            WHERE runs.id IN {run_ids}
 981            """)
 982
 983        if not query.exec():
 984            raise SyntaxError(query.lastError().text())
 985
 986        while query.next():
 987            subset['subjects'].append(query.value(0))
 988            subset['sessions'].append(query.value(1))
 989            subset['runs'].append(query.value(2))
 990
 991        data_path = QFileDialog.getExistingDirectory()
 992        if data_path == '':
 993            return
 994
 995        progress = QProgressDialog('', 'Cancel', 0, len(subset['runs']), self)
 996        progress.setWindowTitle('Converting to BIDS')
 997        progress.setMinimumDuration(0)
 998        progress.setWindowModality(Qt.WindowModal)
 999
1000        create_bids(self.db, Path(data_path), deface=False, subset=subset, progress=progress)
1001        progress.setValue(len(subset['runs']))
